'''1,4-二(三氟甲基)苯'''是一种[[有机化合物|有机化合物]]，化学式为C<sub>8</sub>H<sub>4</sub>F<sub>6</sub>。它可由[[4-三氟甲基苯硼酸|4-三氟甲基苯硼酸]]和[[三氟甲基亚铜|三氟甲基亚铜]]（或其配合物<ref>Roman, Daniela Sustac. (1,​10-​Phenanthroline)​(trifluoromethyl)​(triphenylphosphine)​copper. ''e-EROS Encyclopedia of Reagents for Organic Synthesis'', 2014. ISBN 978-0-470-84289-8.</ref>）反应制得。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Chemistry - A European Journal|volume=19|issue=52|language=en|date=2013-12-23|pages=17692–17697|doi=10.1002/chem.201303828|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1002/chem.201303828|title=Direct Synthesis of a Trifluoromethyl Copper Reagent from Trifluoromethyl Ketones: Application to Trifluoromethylation|accessdate=2020-10-22|author=Hiroki Serizawa, Kohsuke Aikawa, Koichi Mikami}}</ref>[[三氟乙酸钠|三氟乙酸钠]]也可作为三氟甲基化试剂与对三氟甲基碘苯反应，得到1,4-二(三氟甲基)苯。<ref>Carr, Gillian E.; Chambers, Richard D.; Holmes, Thomas F.; Parker, David G. Sodium perfluoroalkanecarboxylates as sources of perfluoroalkyl groups. ''Journal of the Chemical Society, Perkin Transactions 1:  Organic and Bio-Organic Chemistry (1972-1999)'', 1988. 4: 921-926. ISSN: 0300-922X.</ref>它在[[硫酸|硫酸]]-[[三氟乙酸|三氟乙酸]]中回流后加入[[N-溴代丁二酰亚胺|NBS]]反应，可以得到1,4-二溴-2,5-二(三氟甲基)苯。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|volume=132|issue=3|language=en|issn=0002-7863|date=2010-01-27|pages=1127–1136|doi=10.1021/ja9092715|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/ja9092715|title=Functionalization in Flexible Porous Solids: Effects on the Pore Opening and the Host−Guest Interactions|accessdate=2020-10-22|author=Thomas Devic, Patricia Horcajada, Christian Serre, Fabrice Salles, Guillaume Maurin, Béatrice Moulin, Daniela Heurtaux, Guillaume Clet, Alexandre Vimont, Jean-Marc Grenèche, Benjamin Le Ouay, Florian Moreau, Emmanuel Magnier, Yaroslav Filinchuk, Jerôme Marrot, Jean-Claude Lavalley, Marco Daturi, Gérard Férey|archive-date=2020-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201008121739/https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/ja9092715|dead-url=no}}</ref>它和[[三溴化硼|三溴化硼]]在[[四氯化碳|四氯化碳]]中反应，可以得到1,4-二(三溴甲基)苯。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Chemical Papers|volume=63|issue=1|issn=1336-9075|date=2009-01-01|doi=10.2478/s11696-008-0082-3|url=http://www.degruyter.com/view/j/chempap.2009.63.issue-1/s11696-008-0082-3/s11696-008-0082-3.xml|title=Mild and efficient conversion of trifluoromethylarenes into tribromomethylarenes using boron tribromide|accessdate=2020-10-22|author=Hongbiao Chen, Jianxiang Yin, Yuanbin Lin|archive-date=2020-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200212100610/https://www.degruyter.com/view/j/chempap.2009.63.issue-1/s11696-008-0082-3/s11696-008-0082-3.xml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

